env.installPhase:
mkdir -p $out/bin $out/nix-support

wrap() {
  local dst="$1"
  local wrapper="$2"
  export prog="$3"
  substituteAll "$wrapper" "$out/bin/$dst"
  chmod +x "$out/bin/$dst"
}
echo $bintools_bin > $out/nix-support/orig-bintools

ldPath="/nix/store/5ras8lrqj24zjmijdzjjqxhlsjif3mr2-binutils-2.35.1/bin"
if [ -e $ldPath/as ]; then
  ln -s $ldPath/as $out/bin/as
fi

wrap ld /nix/store/756xysvbjqz0pkrkah9zld89lya22gjb-ld-wrapper.sh ${ld:-$ldPath/ld}

for variant in ld.gold ld.bfd ld.lld; do
  local underlying=$ldPath/$variant
  [[ -e "$underlying" ]] || continue
  wrap $variant /nix/store/756xysvbjqz0pkrkah9zld89lya22gjb-ld-wrapper.sh $underlying
done
env.name: binutils-wrapper-2.35.1
env.postFixup:
touch "$out/nix-support/libc-ldflags"
echo "-L/nix/store/rcpa541l40skjbsz1rh7wll05ra5cbv7-bootstrap-stage0-glibc/lib" >> $out/nix-support/libc-ldflags

echo "/nix/store/rcpa541l40skjbsz1rh7wll05ra5cbv7-bootstrap-stage0-glibc" > $out/nix-support/orig-libc
echo "/nix/store/rcpa541l40skjbsz1rh7wll05ra5cbv7-bootstrap-stage0-glibc" > $out/nix-support/orig-libc-dev
if [[ -z ${dynamicLinker+x} ]]; then
  echo "Don't know the name of the dynamic linker for platform 'x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu', so guessing instead." >&2
  local dynamicLinker="/nix/store/rcpa541l40skjbsz1rh7wll05ra5cbv7-bootstrap-stage0-glibc/lib/ld*.so.?"
fi
dynamicLinker=($dynamicLinker)

case ${#dynamicLinker[@]} in
  0) echo "No dynamic linker found for platform 'x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu'." >&2;;
  1) echo "Using dynamic linker: '$dynamicLinker'" >&2;;
  *) echo "Multiple dynamic linkers found for platform 'x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu'." >&2;;
esac

if [ -n "${dynamicLinker-}" ]; then
  echo $dynamicLinker > $out/nix-support/dynamic-linker

  if [ -e /nix/store/rcpa541l40skjbsz1rh7wll05ra5cbv7-bootstrap-stage0-glibc/lib/32/ld-linux.so.2 ]; then
  echo /nix/store/rcpa541l40skjbsz1rh7wll05ra5cbv7-bootstrap-stage0-glibc/lib/32/ld-linux.so.2 > $out/nix-support/dynamic-linker-m32
fi
touch $out/nix-support/ld-set-dynamic-linker

fi
printWords /nix/store/5ras8lrqj24zjmijdzjjqxhlsjif3mr2-binutils-2.35.1 /nix/store/rcpa541l40skjbsz1rh7wll05ra5cbv7-bootstrap-stage0-glibc > $out/nix-support/propagated-user-env-packages
ln -s /nix/store/n7l9irl8km17frld9nmsni7ii0dbib2z-binutils-2.35.1-man $man
ln -s /nix/store/mk8f81m4v2np6akn4sdfd5aqpf1pwh3s-binutils-2.35.1-info $info
export hardening_unsupported_flags=""
if [[ "$($ldPath/ld -z now 2>&1 || true)" =~ un(recognized|known)\ option ]]; then
  hardening_unsupported_flags+=" bindnow"
fi
if [[ "$($ldPath/ld -z relro 2>&1 || true)" =~ un(recognized|known)\ option ]]; then
  hardening_unsupported_flags+=" relro"
fi
for flags in "$out/nix-support"/*flags*; do
  substituteInPlace "$flags" --replace $'\n' ' '
done

substituteAll /nix/store/mrzpfh0ml9k07sw019ydagbb2z1q4sxz-add-flags.sh $out/nix-support/add-flags.sh
substituteAll /nix/store/qzsa3s8dzhyq54jagim4daz1ic2mshfz-add-hardening.sh $out/nix-support/add-hardening.sh
substituteAll /nix/store/99l0a6z7m309b34y4qcz9x1marlsj05p-utils.bash $out/nix-support/utils.bash
